Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界真正的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这单片眼镜借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称为「坂井悠二」的人类究竟是不是火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请自己去确认吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为要现在你来协助我们看来是没可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像小姐这样在这个城市土生土长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保留着这个城市纯粹的印象的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才适合进行调律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学是火炬的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学没事的…一定没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在明天的祭典上一定要对坂井同学说「我喜欢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,8)}{\bord2\1c&H3535FF&\3c&HCFCFCF&}破碎的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把目标放在悠二身上的「扮装舞会」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混进这城市里的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里原本已经不平衡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变得更糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不能再待在这城市里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没有「扮装舞会」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也已经不是人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天必须和母亲以及大家分别
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想暂时在这里…和平时一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天穿上和服让悠二大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一起去祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了离开这里的时候也…一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起离开这城市？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈  这还真是迷得彻底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们  应该明白这意味着什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的目标就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能使用这个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就带我们走是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试看就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不是绕着圈子叫我们别跟去呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换作平时的你不就一顿臭揍了结的嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样看来明天会下酒雨咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 祭典穿不穿和服去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为买新的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说要离开这城市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是…害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天5点在桥那里碰头怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那小姑娘如何了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫坂井悠二的男人不是火炬便好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  能冷静到可以帮忙的程度就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调律这城市稍微有点麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 歪曲得异常严重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  在这附近也打上印记好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再打一两个应该够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过 不光是歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有某些不协和感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止可谓是一帆风顺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离准备完成还剩6小时14分32秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这花纹非常合适
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见这么漂亮的小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠真得会吓一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但小悠好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经有离开城市的心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却很痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  已经那么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 等很久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠怎么搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期六一直是下午开始锻炼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会早回来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和他说过今天晚上开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去祭典的事没告诉过他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是闲逛去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闲逛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去找小悠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和池他们在缘日玩也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}缘日：参拜神佛的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下便条的话就算错过也不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里遇见的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠会更吃惊也说不定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜 看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是苹果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠缘日来的话绝对会买的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃吃看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要妨碍我们训练
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是来祭典玩的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人说要出门的话就乖乖跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且啊  再那样继续的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会做出一道难看的活「人」刺身咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荣太  去买点酒来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝酒么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方 走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店还真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有苹果糖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想知道…坂井同学到底有没有事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…这样下去就…永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  剩下的就是等待那位小姐的协助了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  仍然很介意这不协和感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是歪曲太厉害的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有红世之徒的气息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前为止还没有办法对付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真~~~是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类还真好用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连一个火焰之雾都没察觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授  准备完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优秀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就对坂井同学好好说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我喜欢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来都没任何气息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草 我想起还有件事要办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是红世之徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但放出了自在式却没有气息是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概藏在什么地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 放松心情就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我们去玻璃檀就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要查出红世之徒的位置就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全给看穿了呵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用法已经知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  不是真打算带他们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是临时应急用用罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平时一样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说也需要用玻璃檀来调查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这自在式还真大手笔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设下这么大的机关  看来不是普通人物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二也一定察觉到了 到底跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是红世之徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先要通知夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田…同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人…坂井同学…骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…宝具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田一美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么吉田一美会和悠二在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:14:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被吉田同学知道了我是火炬的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快去追她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事…别去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧  红世之徒开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须对吉田同学解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二一定要和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要对吉田一美那种人解释
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们无关的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无关？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和吉田一美毫无关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么都没所谓啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到夏娜会说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说并不是无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「仪装的收集者」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好久不见了呢「天壤之劫火」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也被这自在式…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸子西亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总对这乱七八糟的自在式有不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…「探耽求究」——旦塔里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是那个神经病教授没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那家伙的气息完~~全感觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来更加需要玻璃檀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧一点吧  启作 荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中那家伙跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走散了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绪什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不说给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才和你在一起的女人的事就不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了只是认识而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:17:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说这的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在蒙混了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…小绪 我可要生气咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么突然说这种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我介意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我介意啊…非常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说到底为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为喜欢田中荣太！所以才介意呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意见吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学是…火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学  到底谁把这种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红世之徒的攻击可已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 继续刚才的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这自在式使得歪曲更厉害了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城市将会被严重到不能修复的歪曲给吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底为了什么而这么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有对策吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 只要开始调律就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必要的印记已经打完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需一位能将城市正常姿态印象化的协助者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 实际上已经有心目中的人选了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微出了点纰漏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫作吉田一美的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 她身上带着的气息原来是你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要她来的话调律马上就能开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为火焰之雾的使命会好好完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该是火焰之雾们来捣乱的时候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白了没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 开始着手第二作战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封绝
